    "diagnosis_summary": "The DNS container has crashed, which is the most likely root cause of the service disruption.",
    "diagnosis_root_cause": "The 'dns' container, which provides essential name resolution for all IMS network functions, has exited. Without DNS, IMS components cannot resolve each other's hostnames (FQDNs), leading to failures in SIP routing and Diameter queries.",
    "diagnosis_affected_components": [
      "dns",
